OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with clear spells. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier overnight with a few
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain over the south,
OL,9,Fstaying dry with some clear intervals
OL,10,Fand a slight frost in the north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FMostly cloudy in the morning
OL,13,Fwith occasional rain. Mainly dry in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon with some brightness in
OL,15,Fthe north and east at times.
