OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with showers and at times
OL,7,Flonger spells of heavier rain, still
OL,8,Fplenty of dry and bright spells
OL,9,Fthough. Winds strengthening Tuesday
OL,10,Fand staying mostly strong Wednesday
OL,11,Fand Thursday.
